Name: CryptoZoo
About the game: ...the best CryptoZoo on the market... the best of it's kind... the best there ever will be... JOIN THE DISCORD Keep up with any other game releases coming your way! THE GAME XD Tokens are a must have for any CryptoZoo-ologist. Use XD Tokens to crack eggs and collect animals. Merge them into new creations and sell high! Hatch-Merge-Sell is the gameplay loop. Short on cash? Cannot afford to crack anymore eggs? Fear not! CryptoZoo includes a in-game mini game called Crypto Invaders to help you earn by playing the game! PLAY TO EARN Destroy waves of Space Cryptos - the further you go. The more XD Tokens you will earn! THE DEVELOPER Coding video games is only a hobby. I work 40 hours a week in the trades. It brings me enjoyment. I love it. And I hope my game(s) bring you enjoyment too! That is what gaming it all about. Have fun :)
